    <content index="9" type="textArea">
Althogh Draconic Evolution for 1.10.2 is now in a stable release state the update is still far from finished. So if you find that something which was avalible in 1.7 is nolonger avalible in 1.10 it probably has not been updated yet. I plan to update almost everything that was in 1.7 so dont be concerned if some of your favorite items/blocks dont exist yet.</content>
    <content alignment="CENTER" index="8" shadow="true" size="1" type="heading">§nImportant!</content>
    <content index="7" size="8" type="vSpacer"/>
    <content alignment="LEFT" index="6" type="splitContainer" vAlignment="BOTTOM" width="10">
        <content alignment="LEFT" index="0" splitSide="RIGHT" type="textArea">§1§a
-Powerful tools and armor

-Teleportation

-Time and weather control

-Mob Farming

-The most over powered energy storage of any mod currently in existance.

-Extreme(ly Dangerous) power generation

-Fancy Effects! (Because that's an important feature!)

-One of the most powerful bosses in modded minecraft</content>
    </content>
    <content index="5" type="textArea">Draconic Evolution is a mod that focuses mainly on extreamely powerful end game tools, weapons an machines.

While at the same time maintaining balance (Althogh this can be tricky) with equally expensive recipes and very difficult bosses which you need to go though in order to get these items.

But this mod started more like an Open Blocks or Extra Utilities type mod so it also has a lot of seemingly random but useful blocs and items.

Some of the key features of this mod are: </content>
    <content index="4" size="8" type="vSpacer"/>
    <content alignment="CENTER" index="3" shadow="true" size="0" type="heading">Now not quiet as OP!!!</content>
